      "text": [
        " اَللَّهِ عَزَّ وَ جَلَّ «ثُمَّ لْيَقْضُوا تَفَثَهُمْ» قَالَ «اَلتَّفَثُ لِقَاءُ اَلْإِمَامِ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3031 - Dharih al-Muharibi narrated from Abu Abdullah (as) regarding the saying of Allah (swt), the Almighty: \"Then let them complete their prescribed duties\" (Surah Al-Hajj 22:29).\nImam (as) said: \"The prescribed duties refer to meeting the Imam.\""
        ]
      }
